Reasoning: The paper deals with capacity and degree-of-freedom scaling for communication channels, specifically in the context of OFDM with amplitude constraint. This falls under the broad category of information theory and communication (cs.IT) and communication and networking (cs.COMM). The use of convex geometry and semi-definite programming (SDP) also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the sub-categories of signal processing (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the mention of numerical simulations suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-category of numerical analysis (cs.NA).
